OL,3,CMum breathes 'sigh of relief' as son
OL,4,Cgets top grades despite school RAAC
OL,5,Cimpact
OL,7,FA mum of a County Durham boy whose
OL,8,Fschool building was largely closed due
OL,9,Fto the substandard concrete RAAC, is
OL,10,Fbreathing "a big sigh of relief" after
OL,11,Fhe received top A-level results after
OL,12,Fa "year from hell".
OL,14,FNicola Cook, 53, whose 18-year-old son
OL,15,Fattended St Leonard's Catholic School
OL,16,Fin Durham, told the PA News Agency
OL,17,Fthat her child achieved his results
OL,18,Fdespite a year of disruption.
