OL,3,CMum breathes 'sigh of relief' as son
OL,4,Cgets top grades despite school RAAC
OL,5,Cimpact
OL,7,FIt is after reinforced autoclaved
OL,8,Faerated concrete (RAAC) was found in
OL,9,Fthe school building, which meant
OL,10,Fstudents were forced to have remote
OL,11,Flessons and in alternative venues.
OL,13,FMs Cook did not name her son but said
OL,14,Fhe was predicted three A*s. On
OL,15,FThursday 15 August, he achieved those
OL,16,Fgrades in psychology and media as well
OL,17,Fas an A in music.
OL,19,F"Overall, it's a big, big sigh of
OL,20,Frelief," Ms Cook said.
