OL,3,CMum breathes 'sigh of relief' as son
OL,4,Cgets top grades despite school RAAC
OL,5,Cimpact
OL,7,FAccording Ms Cook, the morning had
OL,8,Fbeen filled with "quite a lot of
OL,9,Ftears" among students "because the
OL,10,Fanxiety has been so great."
OL,12,FShe added: "He got that win on his
OL,13,Fabsolute own merit, down to his
OL,14,Fresilience and his hard work and the
OL,15,Fexceptional hard work of the teachers
OL,16,Fin that school.
OL,18,F"You cannot diminish the impact that
OL,19,Fthe last year has had, mentally as
OL,20,Fwell as academically, on these
OL,21,Fchildren."
