OL,3,CMum breathes 'sigh of relief' as son
OL,4,Cgets top grades despite school RAAC
OL,5,Cimpact
OL,7,FMs Cook's son, who has autism, will
OL,8,Fnow be going on to psychology at the
OL,9,FUniversity of York.
OL,11,FThroughout the year pupils at St
OL,12,FLeonard's Catholic School were taught
OL,13,Fin various locations around Durham,
OL,14,Fdue to the presence of aerated
OL,15,Fconcrete.
