OL,3,CMum breathes 'sigh of relief' as son
OL,4,Cgets top grades despite school RAAC
OL,5,Cimpact
OL,7,FAccording to Ms Cook, these included
OL,8,Fan office building in a nearby town, a
OL,9,F"non-soundproof" converted sports hall
OL,10,Fon the school grounds, and in a
OL,11,Fconference room at the Radisson Hotel
OL,12,Fin Durham, in which several lessons
OL,13,Ftook place concurrently.
OL,15,F"For the first full term, the kids
OL,16,Fcouldn't even get access to their
OL,17,Ftextbooks or their previous
OL,18,Fcoursework, or if you had a musical
OL,19,Finstrument in the music department,
OL,20,Fyou couldn't even get that back," she
OL,21,Fadded.
