OL,3,CMum breathes 'sigh of relief' as son
OL,4,Cgets top grades despite school RAAC
OL,5,Cimpact
OL,7,F"The temporary accommodation to
OL,8,Frehouse the school wasn't usable until
OL,9,Fafter Easter, so our kids have had a
OL,10,Fyear from hell.
OL,12,F"The minute the school was closed, all
OL,13,Fchildren with SEND needs lost all
OL,14,Freasonable adjustments, because it
OL,15,Fjust wasn't the environment to provide
OL,16,Fthem."
OL,18,FMs Cook, a company director, spoke of
OL,19,Fhow her son's mental health suffered
OL,20,Fdrastically and he needed to get
OL,21,Fmental health support.
OL,26,@xD@FOU
