OL,3,CMum breathes 'sigh of relief' as son
OL,4,Cgets top grades despite school RAAC
OL,5,Cimpact
OL,7,F"Thankfully, the school was very aware
OL,8,Fand was able to support him because
OL,9,Fhis depression and anxiety was off the
OL,10,Fscale, so it's been a really tense
OL,11,Ftime," she said.
OL,13,FA report by academics in January
OL,14,Fcalled for pupils at schools where
OL,15,Fteaching had been badly affected by
OL,16,Fthe Raac crisis ` such as St Leonard's
OL,17,FCatholic School ` to have their exam
OL,18,Fresults lifted by up to 10%.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
