OL,7,FHowever pupils in exam years who faced
OL,8,Fdisruption to their learning and
OL,9,Fteaching due to RAAC were not granted
OL,10,Fthis dispensation.
OL,12,FSt Leonard's Catholic School and the
OL,13,FConservative Party have been
OL,14,Fapproached for comment.
